			GROUP BY aa.wave_no
		) as c on c.wave_no=a.wave_no
		left join (select wh,name as wh_name from u13123456789_my_wh) as d on d.wh=a.wh

1573189470--SELECT a.system_id,c.system_name,COUNT(1) AS counts, b.nums, SUM(deposit_money) AS total_deposit, SUM(express_money) AS total_express, SUM(take_price) AS take_money, SUM(other_money) AS other_money, SUM(prd_money) AS prd_express, a.ADDDATE, d.balance FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log AS a 
				INNER JOIN (
					SELECT system_id,ADDDATE,balance FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log m
					INNER JOIN (
						SELECT MAX(id) AS id FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log where system_id = '' and addtime > '' and addtime < '1575781470'  GROUP BY ADDDATE 
					) n ON n.id = m.id
				) d ON a.ADDDATE = d.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN (SELECT system_id,COUNT(1) AS nums,ADDDATE FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log WHERE tid LIKE 'CZ%' GROUP BY system_id,ADDDATE) b
				ON a.system_id = b.system_id and a.ADDDATE = b.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN u13123456789_drop_shipping_client c ON a.system_id = c.system_id
				 where 1=1
				GROUP BY a.system_id,a.adddate ORDER BY a.ADDTIME DESC limit 0,50
1573189470--SELECT a.system_id,c.system_name,COUNT(1) AS counts, b.nums, SUM(deposit_money) AS total_deposit, SUM(express_money) AS total_express, SUM(take_price) AS take_money, SUM(other_money) AS other_money, SUM(prd_money) AS prd_express, a.ADDDATE, d.balance FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log AS a 
				INNER JOIN (
					SELECT system_id,ADDDATE,balance FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log m
					INNER JOIN (
						SELECT MAX(id) AS id FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log where system_id = '' and addtime > '' and addtime < '1575781470'  GROUP BY ADDDATE 
					) n ON n.id = m.id
				) d ON a.ADDDATE = d.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN (SELECT system_id,COUNT(1) AS nums,ADDDATE FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log WHERE tid LIKE 'CZ%' GROUP BY system_id,ADDDATE) b
				ON a.system_id = b.system_id and a.ADDDATE = b.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN u13123456789_drop_shipping_client c ON a.system_id = c.system_id

1573192534--SELECT a.id, a.wh, a.prd_loc, a.prd_id, a.prd_sku_id, ifnull(e.prd_no,a.prd_no) AS prd_no_sku_no, ifnull(concat(f.sku_name1,';',f.sku_name2),a.sku_name) as sku_names, a.bat_no, a.qty, a.bat_qty+ifnull(b.nums,0) as nums, c.name AS wh_name,d.name AS loc_name, d.is_explosion, e.title, e.sort_name, ifnull(nullif(f.pic_path,''),e.pic_path) as pic_path, f.prd_sku_no, ifnull(nullif(f.cost_price,''),e.cost_price) as cost_price,ifnull(nullif(f.cost_price,''),e.cost_price) as cost_price FROM u13123456789_prdt_wms_qty AS a 
		LEFT JOIN (
			SELECT prd_loc,wh,prd_no,sku_name,prd_id,prd_sku_id,COUNT(id) AS nums FROM u13123456789_prdt_serial_no
			WHERE send_type in (0,3)
			GROUP BY prd_loc,wh,prd_no,prd_id,prd_sku_id,sku_name
		) AS b ON a.prd_loc=b.prd_loc AND a.wh=b.wh and (a.prd_id<>'' and a.prd_id = b.prd_id AND  a.prd_sku_id = b.prd_sku_id or a.prd_id='' and a.prd_no=b.prd_no and a.sku_name=b.sku_name)
		LEFT JOIN u13123456789_my_wh c ON a.wh = c.wh
		LEFT JOIN u13123456789_wh_loc d ON a.prd_loc = d.prd_loc
		LEFT JOIN u13123456789_product e ON  a.prd_id = e.prd_id
		LEFT JOIN u13123456789_product_sku f ON a.prd_sku_id = f.prd_sku_id
		where (a.qty <> 0 or b.nums <> 0)  and left(a.prd_loc,1)<>'@' limit 0,50

1573192534--SELECT a.qty ,ifnull(nullif(f.cost_price,''),e.cost_price) as cost_price FROM u13123456789_prdt_wms_qty AS a 
				LEFT JOIN (
				SELECT prd_loc,wh,prd_no,sku_name,prd_id,prd_sku_id,COUNT(id) AS nums FROM u13123456789_prdt_serial_no
				WHERE send_type in (0,3)
				GROUP BY prd_loc,wh,prd_no,prd_id,prd_sku_id,sku_name
			) AS b ON a.prd_loc=b.prd_loc AND a.wh=b.wh and (a.prd_id<>'' and a.prd_id = b.prd_id AND  a.prd_sku_id = b.prd_sku_id or a.prd_id='' and a.prd_no=b.prd_no and a.sku_name=b.sku_name)
			LEFT JOIN u13123456789_my_wh c ON a.wh = c.wh
			LEFT JOIN u13123456789_wh_loc d ON a.prd_loc = d.prd_loc
			LEFT JOIN u13123456789_product e ON  a.prd_id = e.prd_id
			LEFT JOIN u13123456789_product_sku f ON a.prd_sku_id = f.prd_sku_id
			where (a.qty <> 0 or b.nums <> 0)  and left(a.prd_loc,1)<>'@'
